nodes.text: Joe Alaskey (April 17, 1952 – February 3, 2016) was an American stand-up comedian, actor, voice artist, and impressionist who provided the voice of the Important Merchant, the Interpreter and Watto's flunky in the Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace video game.
